A quick rundown of the system:

cortex.py:
  Is the main file, and contains the Controller class.
  The Controller is used for initialization.


Data       -- The external data that we want to monitor for updates
-------------------------------------------------------------------
Sources    -- Specify data locations, data type, and other parameters
Readers    -- Generic interfaces for retrieving various types of data
Containers -- Use 1 or more readers to retrieve data and pass it on to..
Store      -- Stores the data locally
View       -- Presents data from the store to the user

Interface  -- Dynamically change sources
